00:00:02.311 --> 00:00:06.279
Welcome to nishamadhulika.com

00:00:06.521 --> 00:00:09.307
Today we will make raw mango chutney.

00:00:09.518 --> 00:00:15.423
Kache aam ki chutney can be served with Samosa, Kachori or Pakoras.

00:00:15.753 --> 00:00:23.686
It also enhances the taste of lunch or dinner when served along with it.

00:00:24.056 --> 00:00:29.842
Let see what are ingredients we require to prepare Kache aam ki chutney.

00:00:30.444 --> 00:00:32.420
Raw mango - 1

00:00:32.787 --> 00:00:37.263
Chopped coriander - 2 cups

00:00:38.031 --> 00:00:41.357
Mint leaves - 1/2 cup

00:00:41.710 --> 00:00:43.773
Heeng (Asafoetida) - 2 pinces

00:00:44.276 --> 00:00:48.133
Salt - 1/2 tsp or according to taste

00:00:48.669 --> 00:00:51.337
Black salt - 1/2 tsp

00:00:51.847 --> 00:00:54.164
Roasted Zeera - 1 tsp

00:00:54.468 --> 00:00:56.380
Ginger - A piece of 1 inch

00:00:56.678 --> 00:00:58.718
Green chilli - 3 to 4

00:00:59.411 --> 00:01:08.566
Peel the raw mango first to prepare the chutney of raw mango.

00:01:15.479 --> 00:01:18.359
Take out its pulp.

00:01:23.709 --> 00:01:25.916
Make the small pieces of pulp.

00:01:29.752 --> 00:01:34.300
We have already prepared coriander and mint leaves.

00:01:35.296 --> 00:01:43.999
Put pieces of raw mango, coriander and mint leaves.

00:01:46.847 --> 00:01:50.982
Make smaller pieces of the piece of ginger.

00:01:58.765 --> 00:02:10.340
Also add green chilli, ginger, roasted zeera, black salt, common salt and Heeng.

00:02:12.908 --> 00:02:14.360
Add half cup water in it.

00:02:18.723 --> 00:02:21.406
Grind the chutney to make it a fine paste.

00:02:37.250 --> 00:02:42.750
The fine paste of chutney is now prepared.

00:02:43.798 --> 00:02:48.305
The mouth-watering and aromatic chutney is now ready.

00:02:48.659 --> 00:02:55.521
You should prepare this chutney whenever you are preparing Samosa, Kachori or Pakore.

00:02:55.818 --> 00:03:03.707
You can prepare this chutney at home and can be taken with meals.

00:03:03.866 --> 00:03:08.763
We can use for 7 days when kept in refrigerator.

00:03:09.261 --> 00:03:15.079
